<h1>Your Job Was Claimed</h1>
<p>Hi,</p>
<p>A technician has claimed your job "<strong><%= @job.title %></strong>". The job is theirs—no action needed from you.</p>
<% if @technician %>
  <p>Technician: <%= @technician.user&.email || @technician.trade_type %></p>
<% end %>
<% if @job.job_amount_cents.to_i > 0 %>
  <p>Your card was charged the job amount + 5% platform fee. Funds are held until the job is complete.</p>
<% end %>
<p>You can message them with questions, or deny them from the job page if needed (this will reopen the job and refund any payment).</p>
<p>— TechFlash</p>
